[
    {
        "text": "The fruit of the cacao tree is a football-shaped pod that comes in a variety of colors.",
        "startTime": 2797,
        "endTime": 7905,
        "slowStartTime": 4345,
        "slowEndTime": 12083
    },
    {
        "text": "Inside each pod is a sweet, white, fruity pulp that covers 50 to 60 seeds.",
        "startTime": 8615,
        "endTime": 14495,
        "slowStartTime": 13073,
        "slowEndTime": 21967
    },
    {
        "text": "It is from these seeds that chocolate is made.",
        "startTime": 15093,
        "endTime": 17733,
        "slowStartTime": 22790,
        "slowEndTime": 26824
    },
    {
        "text": "Once the pods are ripe, they are harvested in the same way they have been gathered...",
        "startTime": 18658,
        "endTime": 23172,
        "slowStartTime": 28137,
        "slowEndTime": 34983
    },
    {
        "text": "...for thousands of years: by hand.",
        "startTime": 23349,
        "endTime": 25803,
        "slowStartTime": 35174,
        "slowEndTime": 38929
    },
    {
        "text": "After collecting the pods, each one is split open.",
        "startTime": 26253,
        "endTime": 29405,
        "slowStartTime": 39529,
        "slowEndTime": 44333
    },
    {
        "text": "Then the farmer scoops out the white pulp and separates the seeds,...",
        "startTime": 30048,
        "endTime": 33902,
        "slowStartTime": 45222,
        "slowEndTime": 51078
    },
    {
        "text": "...commonly known as \"cocoa beans.\"",
        "startTime": 34347,
        "endTime": 36371,
        "slowStartTime": 51671,
        "slowEndTime": 54781
    },
    {
        "text": "The beans are covered with banana leaves or burlap while they ferment in the pulp.",
        "startTime": 37007,
        "endTime": 41366,
        "slowStartTime": 55660,
        "slowEndTime": 62274
    },
    {
        "text": "After fermenting, the beans are uncovered and dried in the hot sun.",
        "startTime": 42234,
        "endTime": 46600,
        "slowStartTime": 63501,
        "slowEndTime": 70125
    },
    {
        "text": "When the beans have achieved maximum dryness, it's time to go to market.",
        "startTime": 47291,
        "endTime": 51549,
        "slowStartTime": 71087,
        "slowEndTime": 77549
    },
    {
        "text": "The farmer puts them in burlap sacks in which they will be sold...",
        "startTime": 52519,
        "endTime": 55945,
        "slowStartTime": 78929,
        "slowEndTime": 84142
    },
    {
        "text": "...and shipped to chocolate factories around the world.",
        "startTime": 56163,
        "endTime": 59240,
        "slowStartTime": 84395,
        "slowEndTime": 89085
    }
]